== 制作 ==
[[File:MichaelJacksonSnoopyKBFApr1984cropped.jpg|thumb]]
杰克逊于1982年6月开始录制《{{lang|en|E.T.}}外星人》的有声书，他大约也就是在这个时候开始录制自己的第六张录音室专辑《[[顫慄_(麥可·傑克森專輯)|顫慄]]》。这两个项目都是由昆西·琼斯担任[[音樂製作人|制作人]]，他同时还是有声书的文本作者之一<ref name="pratt">{{cite book | last = Pratt | first = Mary K. | title = Michael Jackson: King of Pop | url = https://archive.org/details/michaeljacksonki0000prat | year = 2010 | publisher = ABDO Publishing | isbn = 1-60453-788-4 | page = [https://archive.org/details/michaeljacksonki0000prat/page/59 59]}}</ref><ref name = "Taraborrelli" />{{rp|209}}。杰克逊在录制旁白的过程中对{{lang|en|E.T.}}的死感到非常沮丧而哭了起来，琼斯和斯皮尔伯格都认为，即使把这部分再录一遍，这位流行歌手也会有一样的情绪反应，所以他们决定就在最终发行的专辑里保留杰克逊的哭声。杰克逊的传记作者丽莎·{{lang|en|D}}·坎贝尔（{{lang|en|Lisa D. Campbell}}）在书中表示，琼斯是在录制专辑《墙外》中的歌曲{{單雙書名號轉換|她离开了我的生活}}时得知此事，杰克逊在演唱这首歌时也流下了[[眼泪|眼泪]]。<ref name="Campbell">{{cite book | last = Campbell | first = Lisa | title = Michael Jackson: The King of Pop | publisher = Branden | year = 1993 | isbn = 0-8283-1957-X}}</ref>{{rp|55}}

多位之前曾参与过杰克逊独唱专辑制作的制作人对《{{lang|en|E.T.}}外星人》故事书专辑作出了贡献。为《墙外》和《顫慄》创作了多首歌曲的[[罗德·坦普顿|罗德·坦普顿]]（{{lang|en|Rod Temperton}}）为歌曲{{單雙書名號轉換|{{lang|en|Someone in the Dark}}}}作曲。[[弗雷迪·德曼|弗雷迪·德曼]]（{{lang|en|Freddy DeMann}}）和杰克逊五人组前经理罗恩·韦斯纳（{{lang|en|Ron Weisner}}）担任专辑的制作协调员。布鲁斯·斯维顿（{{lang|en|Bruce Swedien}}）担任工程师，他也是《墙外》和《顫慄》的工程师，之后还将在杰克逊的《[[棒_(迈克尔·杰克逊专辑)|棒]]》和《[[危险之旅_(迈克尔·杰克逊专辑)|危险之旅]]》两张专辑制作中扮演同一角色。迪克·齐默尔曼（{{lang|en|Dick Zimmerman}}）为杰克逊拍摄了《顫慄》的专辑封面，还拍摄了《{{lang|en|E.T.}}外星人》中{{lang|en|E.T.}}的双手搭在杰克逊肩膀上的海报。<ref name="Campbell" />{{rp|55-56}}

录制和工程制作完成后，{{lang|en|MCA}}唱片公司压制了超过一百万份有声书副本。1982年，《[[告示牌_(杂志)|告示牌]]》杂志的一位[[记者|记者]]称，这是{{lang|en|MCA}}唱片公司当时“最雄心勃勃的”项目之一<ref name="billboard">{{cite news | last = Kozak | first = Roman | title = CBS sues to block MCA 'E.T.' package | url = http://books.google.ca/books?id=0yQEAAAAMBAJ&pg=PP1&lpg=PP1&dq=E.T.+the+Extra-Terrestrial+michael+jackson+billboard&source=bl&ots=_L3ezrjHSB&sig=_GnBCeEyTslIxCnYUX33PSqhpVs&hl=en&sa=X&ei=AMaAT8e_Mc3PrQfdien9BQ&ved=0CDQQ6AEwAw#v=onepage&q=E.T.%20the%20Extra-Terrestrial%20michael%20jackson%20billboard&f=false | accessdate = 2014-02-24 | newspaper = Billboard | date = 1982-11-27 | archive-date = 2014-03-05 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20140305174441/http://books.google.ca/books?id=0yQEAAAAMBAJ&pg=PP1&lpg=PP1&dq=E.T.+the+Extra-Terrestrial+michael+jackson+billboard&source=bl&ots=_L3ezrjHSB&sig=_GnBCeEyTslIxCnYUX33PSqhpVs&hl=en&sa=X&ei=AMaAT8e_Mc3PrQfdien9BQ&ved=0CDQQ6AEwAw#v=onepage&q=E.T.%20the%20Extra-Terrestrial%20michael%20jackson%20billboard&f=false | dead-url = no }}</ref>。

== 杰克逊对{{lang|en|E.T.}}的感情 ==
根据记者{{lang|en|J}}·兰迪·塔拉博雷利（{{lang|en|J. Randy Taraborrelli}}）为杰克逊撰写的传记《迈克尔·杰克逊：魔法与疯狂》（{{lang|en|''Michael Jackson: The Magic and the Madness''}}）记载，杰克逊很早就对{{lang|en|E.T.}}的故事表现出依恋。他在拍摄专辑唱片的宣传照时需要与{{lang|en|E.T.}}的电子动画角色拥抱，之后杰克逊表示：“他是如此真实，我都在和他说话。我离开前亲吻了他，到第二天，我就开始想念他了。”<ref name = "Taraborrelli" />{{rp|209}}杰克逊之后在1982年12月的《{{lang|en|Ebony}}》杂志中透露——杰克逊和{{lang|en|E.T.}}一起出现在这期杂志的封面上——他觉得在专辑录制期间自己就是{{lang|en|E.T.}}，他还表示了自己为什么会与{{lang|en|E.T.}}之间有如此强烈的联系。
<blockquote>
“他身处一个陌生的环境，希望能获得接纳——我在世界各地演出，从一个[[城市|城市]]前往另一个城市时经常有这种感觉。他与孩子们相处最为融洽，而我也非常喜欢孩子。他爱人，也希望被爱，我也是。他还有那种可以让自己前往任何地方，远离这个世界喧嚣和尘埃的超能力，而我也希望能够如此。他和我在许多方面都很相似。”<ref name="Michael" />
</blockquote>

== 发行和法律争议 ==
史诗唱片同意杰克逊与{{lang|en|MCA}}唱片合作录制这张专辑，但有两个条件：
# 《{{lang|en|E.T. the Extra-Terrestrial}}》只能在1982年[[圣诞节|圣诞节]]后再发行（这是为了避免与杰克逊的新专辑《顫慄》竞争）；
# 唱片中的歌曲{{單雙書名號轉換|{{lang|en|Someone in the Dark}}}}不能作为单曲发售。<ref name="Then came 'Thriller'!" />
然而，{{lang|en|MCA}}唱片在1982年11月就发行了《{{lang|en|E.T.外星人}}》，并把{{單雙書名號轉換|{{lang|en|Someone in the Dark}}}}的[[黑胶唱片|黑胶唱片]]推广副本交给了广播电台。史诗唱片于是提起诉讼，并要求200万美元的赔偿，之后{{lang|en|MCA}}唱片被迫从市场上撤回了专辑，法庭也对《{{lang|en|Someone In the Dark}}》的单曲发行下了禁令<ref name="Then came 'Thriller'!" /><ref name="Campbell" />{{rp|55}}<ref name="Grant">{{cite book | last = Grant | first = Adrian | title = Michael Jackson: The Visual Documentary | publisher = Omnibus Press | year = 2009 | isbn = 978-1-84938-261-8 | page = 61}}</ref><ref>"Someone In the Dark" vinyl</ref>。史诗唱片的高管还觉得{{lang|en|MCA}}有意误导了公众，让大家以为当时发行不久的单曲{{單雙書名號轉換|这女孩是我的}}也包含在《{{lang|en|E.T.}}外星人》的专辑中，因此提出永久禁止{{lang|en|MCA}}与杰克逊合作，并且该公司已经拥有的任何杰克逊演绎作品都要禁止发售<ref name="billboard" />。

由于法律禁止{{單雙書名號轉換|{{lang|en|Someone in the Dark}}}}以单曲形式发行，因此其推广副本之后成为杰克逊最稀有也最抢手的唱片之一，其中一些的售价超过1000[[英镑|英镑]]（相当于1660美元）<ref name="Halstead">{{cite book | last = Halstead | first = Craig | title = Michael Jackson: For the Record | url = https://archive.org/details/michaeljacksonfo00cadm | year = 2007 | publisher = AOL | isbn = 978-0-7552-0267-6 | page = [https://archive.org/details/michaeljacksonfo00cadm/page/294 294]}}</ref><ref>{{cite web | title = Pound to Dollar conversion | url = http://www.poundtodollar.co.uk/ | publisher = Poundtodollar.co.uk | accessdate = 2014-02-24 | archive-date = 2014-02-28 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20140228050643/http://www.poundtodollar.co.uk/ | dead-url = no }}</ref>。这首歌之后以附赠曲目形式出现在2001年的《顫慄》特别版中，还出现在《迈克尔·杰克逊：终极收藏》套装中<ref name="mtv">{{cite web | last = Orzeck | first = Kurt | title = Michael Jackson's Thriller Reissue: All Killer, No Filler | archivedate = 2014-02-24 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20140224144636/http://www.mtv.com/news/articles/1581358/michael-jacksons-thriller-reissue-more-new-releases.jhtml | url = http://www.mtv.com/news/articles/1581358/michael-jacksons-thriller-reissue-more-new-releases.jhtml | publisher = MTV | date = 2008-02-12 | accessdate = 2014-02-24 | dead-url = no }}</ref><ref name="variety">{{cite web | last = Gallo | first = Phil | title = Anniversary release for 'Thriller' | url = http://variety.com/2007/music/news/anniversary-release-for-thriller-1117976801/ | publisher = ''Variety'' | date = 2007-11-30 | accessdate = 2014-02-24 | archivedate = 2014-02-24 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20140224144130/http://variety.com/2007/music/news/anniversary-release-for-thriller-1117976801/ }}</ref><ref name="popmatters">{{cite web | last = Harris | first = Will | title = Michael Jackson: The Ultimate Collection | url = http://www.popmatters.com/review/jacksonmichael-ultimate/ | publisher = PopMatters | date = 2005-01-05 | accessdate = 2014-02-24 | archivedate = 2014-02-24 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20140224144310/http://www.popmatters.com/review/jacksonmichael-ultimate/ }}</ref>。

== 反响 ==
《{{lang|en|E.T.外星人}}》获得了商业上的成功，在[[英国专辑排行榜|英国专辑排行榜]]上排到第82位<ref name = "rees 258" />，对于一个故事书专辑来说，这已经是非常好的成绩<ref name = "Honeyford">{{cite book | last = Honeyford | first = Paul | title = Thrill of Michael Jackson | url = https://archive.org/details/thrillofmichaelj0000hone | publisher = William Morrow & Co | year = 1984 | isbn = 0-688-04094-2 | page = [https://archive.org/details/thrillofmichaelj0000hone/page/58 58]}}</ref>。杰克逊因这张唱片在第26届[[格莱美奖|格莱美奖]]角逐中赢得了一张最佳儿童唱片奖<ref name="George" />{{rp|40}}<ref name="la1">{{cite web | last = Hilburn | first = Robert | date = 1984-02-29 | title = The Jackson 8: A 'Thriller' at the Grammys | url = http://pqasb.pqarchiver.com/latimes/doc/153746256.html?FMT=ABS&FMTS=ABS:AI&type=historic&date=Feb%2029,%201984&author=&pub=Los%20Angeles%20Times&edition=&startpage=&desc=The%20Jackson%208:%20A%20'Thriller'%20at%20the%20Grammys | publisher = ''Los Angeles Times'' | accessdate = 2014-02-24}}</ref><ref name="la2">{{cite web | last = Hilburn | first = Robert | date = 1984-02-26 | title = Jackson: New King of the Grammy Road? | url = http://pqasb.pqarchiver.com/latimes/doc/153734234.html?FMT=ABS&FMTS=ABS:AI&type=historic&date=Feb%2026,%201984&author=&pub=Los%20Angeles%20Times&edition=&startpage=&desc=JACKSON:%20NEW%20KING%20OF%20THE%20GRAMMY%20ROAD? | publisher = ''Los Angeles Times'' | accessdate = 2014-02-24 | archive-date = 2014-02-28 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20140228185031/http://pqasb.pqarchiver.com/latimes/doc/153734234.html?FMT=ABS&FMTS=ABS%3AAI&type=historic&date=Feb%2026%2C%201984&author=&pub=Los%20Angeles%20Times&edition=&startpage=&desc=JACKSON%3A%20NEW%20KING%20OF%20THE%20GRAMMY%20ROAD%3F | dead-url = no }}</ref>，这届葛莱美奖针对的是1982年10月1日到1983年9月30日期间发行的唱片<ref name=mjgrammy>{{cite web | title = Michael Jackson big Grammy winner | url = http://news.google.com/newspapers?id=OW4sAAAAIBAJ&sjid=4c4EAAAAIBAJ&pg=6904,6865310&dq=grammy+awards+eligibility&hl=en | publisher = ''Spartanburg Herald-Journal'' | date = 1984-02-29 | accessdate = 2014-02-24 | archive-date = 2021-05-09 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20210509053645/https://news.google.com/newspapers?id=OW4sAAAAIBAJ&sjid=4c4EAAAAIBAJ&pg=6904,6865310&dq=grammy+awards+eligibility&hl=en | dead-url = no }}</ref>，杰克逊当晚赢得了空前的12项提名，最终夺得了8项大奖，他表示在这些奖项中，自己“最为这张感到自豪”<ref name="Michael Jackson gets record 12 nominations">{{cite web | url = http://news.google.co.uk/newspapers?id=63QQAAAAIBAJ&sjid=rIsDAAAAIBAJ&pg=4656,1210844&dq=michael-jackson+extra-terrestrial&hl=en | title = Michael Jackson gets record 12 nominations | last = Arar | first = Yardena | date = 1984-01-11 | publisher = ''The Free Lance–Star'' | accessdate = 2014-02-24 | archive-date = 2016-03-05 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20160305095804/https://news.google.co.uk/newspapers?id=63QQAAAAIBAJ&sjid=rIsDAAAAIBAJ&pg=4656,1210844&dq=michael-jackson+extra-terrestrial&hl=en | dead-url = no }}</ref><ref name="Singer Michael Jackson claims 8 music awards">{{cite web | url = http://news.google.co.uk/newspapers?id=ulQHAAAAIBAJ&sjid=xjQDAAAAIBAJ&pg=3058,209235&dq=michael-jackson+extra-terrestrial&hl=en | title = Singer Michael Jackson claims 8 music awards | date = 1984-02-29 | publisher = ''Rome News-Tribune'' | accessdate = 2014-02-24 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20160305072121/https://news.google.co.uk/newspapers?id=ulQHAAAAIBAJ&sjid=xjQDAAAAIBAJ&pg=3058,209235&dq=michael-jackson+extra-terrestrial&hl=en | archive-date = 2016-03-05 | dead-url = yes }}</ref><ref name="A night of records">{{cite web | url = http://news.google.co.uk/newspapers?id=feMPAAAAIBAJ&sjid=hosDAAAAIBAJ&pg=4928,4254108&dq=i-m-most-proud-of-this-one&hl=en | title = A night of records | last = Arar | first = Yardena | date = 1984-02-29 | publisher = ''The Free Lance–Star'' | accessdate = 2014-02-24 | archive-date = 2016-03-05 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20160305152730/https://news.google.co.uk/newspapers?id=feMPAAAAIBAJ&sjid=hosDAAAAIBAJ&pg=4928,4254108&dq=i-m-most-proud-of-this-one&hl=en | dead-url = no }}</ref>。

《{{lang|en|E.T.外星人}}》也获得了评论家的好评。《{{lang|en|Ebony}}》杂志的查尔斯·{{lang|en|L}}·桑德斯（{{lang|en|Charles L Sanders}}）称赞这是一张“非凡的专辑”<ref name="Diana and Michael">{{cite book | url = http://books.google.com/?id=y9gDAAAAMBAJ&pg=PA36&dq=extra-terrestrial+%22michael+jackson%22#v=onepage&q=extra-terrestrial%20%22michael%20jackson%22&f=false | title = Diana and Michael | last = Sanders | first = Charles L. | date = 1983-11 | publisher = ''Ebony'' | accessdate = 2014-02-24 | quote = extraordinary album.}}</ref>。《[[刀锋报|托莱多刀锋报]]》（{{lang|en|''Toledo Blade''}}）的马克·比高（{{lang|en|Mark Bego}}）断言，{{單雙書名號轉換|{{lang|en|Someone in the Dark}}}}是杰克逊所录制过“最美丽的歌谣之一”<ref name="Then came 'Thriller'!" />，他还称赞琼斯在制作中把电影台词、杰克逊阅读文段的真实情感，以及有声书“波澜壮阔的（乐器）编排”融合在一起，让这张唱片“就像电影一样催人泪下”<ref name="Then came 'Thriller'!" />。《告示牌》杂志的一篇文章称这部有声书“包装华丽，制作精良”，虽然价格高昂，但绝对值回票价<ref name="billboard2">{{cite news | title = Top album picks | url = http://books.google.ca/books?id=0yQEAAAAMBAJ&pg=PP1&lpg=PP1&dq=E.T.+the+Extra-Terrestrial+michael+jackson+billboard&source=bl&ots=_L3ezrjHSB&sig=_GnBCeEyTslIxCnYUX33PSqhpVs&hl=en&sa=X&ei=AMaAT8e_Mc3PrQfdien9BQ&ved=0CDQQ6AEwAw#v=onepage&q=E.T.%20the%20Extra-Terrestrial%20michael%20jackson%20billboard&f=false | accessdate = 2014-02-24 | newspaper = Billboard | page = 68 | date = 1982-11-27 | archive-date = 2014-03-05 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20140305174441/http://books.google.ca/books?id=0yQEAAAAMBAJ&pg=PP1&lpg=PP1&dq=E.T.+the+Extra-Terrestrial+michael+jackson+billboard&source=bl&ots=_L3ezrjHSB&sig=_GnBCeEyTslIxCnYUX33PSqhpVs&hl=en&sa=X&ei=AMaAT8e_Mc3PrQfdien9BQ&ved=0CDQQ6AEwAw#v=onepage&q=E.T.%20the%20Extra-Terrestrial%20michael%20jackson%20billboard&f=false | dead-url = no }}</ref>。《[[列克星敦先驱领袖报|列克星敦先驱领袖报]]》（{{lang|en|''Lexington Herald-Leader''}}）总结认为这是一张“令人愉快的”故事书专辑<ref name="Sound tracks enable you to savor the magic from favorite movies">{{cite web | url = http://nl.newsbank.com/nl-search/we/Archives?p_product=LH&s_site=kentucky&p_multi=LH&p_theme=realcities&p_action=search&p_maxdocs=200&p_topdoc=1&p_text_direct-0=0EB73629C3C8B677&p_field_direct-0=document_id&p_perpage=10&p_sort=YMD_date:D&s_trackval=GooglePM | title = Sound tracks enable you to savor the magic from favorite movies | date = 1983-06-09 | publisher = ''Lexington Herald-Leader'' | accessdate = 2014-02-24 | archive-date = 2014-03-04 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20140304212324/http://nl.newsbank.com/nl-search/we/Archives?p_product=LH&s_site=kentucky&p_multi=LH&p_theme=realcities&p_action=search&p_maxdocs=200&p_topdoc=1&p_text_direct-0=0EB73629C3C8B677&p_field_direct-0=document_id&p_perpage=10&p_sort=YMD_date:D&s_trackval=GooglePM | dead-url = no }}</ref>。

